,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T01:29:32.000Z","msg":"燒山個翻譯170國語言俾19撚到而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇黎澳門都有排講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba2c4a6153ddf5913e4dbd1876c01ed6ef2f4ad7","tid":378940,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T01:30:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實個風路徑向北少少就唔係呢回事</blockquote><br />\n個風打得中 打唔中都唔代表澳狗唔係垃圾<br />\n一個季節性既颱風都頂唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可想以知並唔係 一兩個party貪/廢<br />\n係成個地區d人都廢</blockquote><br />\n香港食多幾個呢d風都冇事</blockquote><br />\n個風向北少少香港都唔會有大事，最多係塌樹"},{"pid":"136da1ae0d1362ccb3c9827fc216a42025690dee","tid":378940,"uid":6942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T01:36:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"781259cecb5bae9ce9af32a92e8877ff94f4e1b0","tid":378940,"uid":2997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T01:39:44.000Z","msg":"正撚到"},{"pid":"e671a3c5c3c30ff75a53b3d1a711d20be94c365e","tid":378940,"uid":130513,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T02:05:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8f3dd2404f00c9bf5e6b9cc9e06728d51c01e42f","tid":378940,"uid":56819,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T03:12:31.000Z","msg":"澳門幾時做左香港阿哥？"},{"pid":"8cb4ece749f873645e6500276448fa91ba36fe1e","tid":378940,"uid":121409,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T04:30:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>澳門幾時做左香港阿哥？</blockquote><br />\n背靠祖國，捉緊機遇，發展迅速，躍升呀哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(應該係)"},{"pid":"225f2ca3693c3be19c78b64848264c7c0ab68c06","tid":378940,"uid":121409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T04:31:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>澳門幾時做左香港阿哥？</blockquote><br />\n背靠祖國，捉緊機